title: Bobby Lee
itunes:title: Bobby Lee
description:
Comedian Bobby Lee (MADtv, And Just Like That, Pineapple Express) is back this week and has a bone to pick with Whitney.  He also talks about his relapse, having threesomes with other comedians, and almost getting killed by a boa constrictor.  Then he and Whitney draw genitals.  Check out Bobby's shows BAD FRIENDS and TIGER BELLY wherever you get your podcasts.
